---
// A short tease of who Matt is. Drives traffic to /about.
---

<section class="section border-b border-brand-grey-700">
  <div class="container-site">
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-end md:justify-between gap-8">
      <div class="max-w-xl">
        <p class="text-brand-red text-xs uppercase tracking-widest mb-4" style="font-family: var(--font-mono);">
          About
        </p>
        <p class="text-brand-grey-100 text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed">
          Matt Keenan is a stand-up comedian based in Saint John, NB. He's been
          performing long enough to have opinions about it. His material sits
          somewhere between observed truth and a calm refusal to accept things
          as they are.
        </p>
      </div>
      <a href="/about" class="link-arrow flex-shrink-0">
        More about Matt →
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
